# The dev cluster's build products and state, none of it source:
#
#   guests/    each QEMU guest's persistent hardware: its disks and
#              its firmware's variable store; `make` creates them
#              blank and `make clean` is a factory reset
#   identity/  the cluster's private keys and join token, minted (or
#              adopted) by the identity domain; never in history
#   image/     the assembled boot archives, which bake the identity
#              and manifests above into the OS the guests boot
guests/
identity/
image/
